title: [Mistydeep, Underwater]
description: Shimmering light passing through the turbulent water overhead casts a dappled light and shadows over the sand.  The fat stems of a thicket of bulrushes stand like ranks of spears to the east, serving as home to countless small fish that dart about the safe haven.
paths: Obvious exits: east, southeast, northwest, up
room.location: the northern reaches of the Mistydeep River
